Edgar O. Huber  President of Luxury, Coty Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 6 different industries.55--
Background

		Mr. Edgar O. Huber has been President of Luxury at Coty Inc. since October 4, 2016. Mr. Huber served as the President of Global Markets at Coty Inc. since November 15, 2015 until October 4, 2016. He served as the Chief Executive Officer and President at Lands' End, Inc. from August 01, 2011 to February 16, 2015. He served as an Executive Vice President of Global Business Development of Kate Spade & Company (formerly Liz Claiborne Inc) since February 14, 2011. Mr. Huber ... served as President and Chief Executive Officer of Juicy Couture Inc. from June 2008 to February 2011. He served as President of the Luxury Products Division of L'Oreal USA, Inc., since 2003 and served as its co-President of Kiehi's since 2002. His experience in the Active Cosmetics division makes him very qualified and knowledgeable about developing highly efficacious and unique products. He has over ten years of experience in the cosmetic industry. He served as marketing trainee of L'Oréal group's in the Active Cosmetics Division since 1992 in France. He served as a Director of Lands' End, Inc. from August 2011 to February 1, 2015. He served as Managing Director of La Roche-Posay in Germany since 1994. Mr. Huber served as an Assistant Managing Director of Lancôme France since 1996. He served as Managing Director of Prestige & Collections in France until 1999 and also served as Managing Director of Lancôme. He served as Managing Director of the Luxury Products Division in the UK of Lancôme since 2000. He served as Director at Living Proof, Inc. Mr. Huber received MBA from Hautes Etudes Commerciales, Paris (HEC) and his PhD in Economics from the University of Vienna.Read Full Background




